    "Disagreement between classification decisions was resolved by a third researcher casting a deciding vote.",
    "Questions containing non-plain text elements such as images were excluded as these could not be inputted to the LLM applications.",
    "Every eligible question was inputted into ChatGPT (GPT-3.5 and GPT-4 versions; OpenAI, San Francisco, California, United States of America) between April 29 and May 10, 2023.",
    "The answers provided by GPT-3.5 and GPT-4 were recorded and their whole reply to each question was recorded for further analysis.",
    "If ChatGPT failed to provide a definitive answer, the question was re-trialled up to three times, after which ChatGPT's answer was recorded as 'null' if no answer was provided."
